SYS_FILE_STATUS (ENUM)
SYS_FILE_STATUS (ENUM)
Â¶
TYPE SYS_FILE_STATUS :
File status
Actual file status of the specified file.
InOut:
Name
Comment
FS_OK
File could be opened
FS_NO_FILE
No file available
FS_ILLEGAL_POS
Illegal position in the file
FS_FULL
No more space on the filesystem
FS_EOF
End of file reached
